SIMPLE: nugget
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nugget
<hw>Nug"get</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Earlier
<ets>niggot</ets>, prob. for <ets>nigot</ets>, <ets>an ingot</ets>. See
<er>Ingot</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A lump; a mass, esp. a native
lump of a precious metal; <as>as, a <ex>nugget</ex> of
gold</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Something of value, usually found among many other
less valuable things; -- often used figuratively; <as>as, a
<ex>nugget</ex> of useful information in a sea of data</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nugify</ent>⟦br⟧
